1
00:00:04,920 --> 00:00:07,143
Murakaza neza nanone muri stidiyo y'imfashanyigisho

2
00:00:07,143 --> 00:00:10,606
Tugiye kunyura mu nshamake
y'icyumweru cya gatanu

3
00:00:10,606 --> 00:00:13,556
"Kuvana Inyungu Mu Guhanga Udushya None"

4
00:00:13,871 --> 00:00:19,045
Nkuko mubyibuka, mu cyumweru gishize
twaganiye ku bijyanye no kurinda igitekerezo cyawe

5
00:00:19,425 --> 00:00:23,686
Ikindi kandi, twaganiye ku buryo
wakorera amafaranga bigendeye

6
00:00:23,686 --> 00:00:26,682
ku bafatanyabikorwa bawe

7
00:00:27,011 --> 00:00:29,165
Maze tuganira bijyanye n'amategeko,

8
00:00:29,264 --> 00:00:33,840
Nuko bwa nyuma, twaganiye cyane
ku bijyanye n'ubwiyongere n'imikurire

9
00:00:34,174 --> 00:00:37,871
Cyo reka duhite dutangire tunyure
muri bimwe mu bintu by'ingenzi

10
00:00:37,871 --> 00:00:39,711
byaranze icyumweru gishize.

11
00:00:41,842 --> 00:00:43,633
Twatangiye icyumweru 

12
00:00:43,633 --> 00:00:50,701
tuganira ku mutungo kamere mu
by'ubwenge no kurinda ibitekerezo byawe.

13
00:00:51,488 --> 00:00:54,409
Twaganiye ku itandukaniro hagati
y'umutungo kamere w'ubwenge

14
00:00:54,409 --> 00:00:55,899
n'umutungo wa nyawe.

15
00:00:55,899 --> 00:00:58,204
Twaganiye gato ku bijyanye no kongera ubushake:

16
00:00:58,204 --> 00:01:03,148
Kubera iki ibihugu bigerageza guteza
imbere umutungo kamere w'ubwenge

17
00:01:03,148 --> 00:01:06,023
kandi ni ibihe byiza 
n'ibibi byabyo?

18
00:01:06,023 --> 00:01:10,345
Turangije twarebeye hamwe amoko ane
y'ingenzi y'umutungo kamere w'ubwenge

19
00:01:10,345 --> 00:01:12,948
ushobora kuzakenera
gukoresha mu bihe bya mbere

20
00:01:12,948 --> 00:01:14,620
bw'izamuka ry'ikigo cyawe cy'imari

21
00:01:14,620 --> 00:01:17,272
Ubwo, twahereye ku mabanga y'ubucuruzi

22
00:01:17,272 --> 00:01:20,432
aribwo bwoko bw'ibanga bukunda
kuboneka, burangwa no kugira

23
00:01:20,432 --> 00:01:23,743
ikintu ibanga maze ukabwira
buri wese ko ari ibanga.

24
00:01:24,340 --> 00:01:27,868
Noneho twaganiye ibijyanye na "trademark",
akaba ari ikimenyetso gihagarariye

25
00:01:27,868 --> 00:01:30,158
ikigo cy'ubucuruzi cyawe n'imikorere yacyo.

26
00:01:30,800 --> 00:01:33,415
Turangije tujya ku byitwa "patents"

27
00:01:33,415 --> 00:01:39,463
zo zikaba zihagarariye, akenshi,
ibicuruzwa bifatika

28
00:01:39,667 --> 00:01:44,741
ariko zikaba zishobora no guhagararira
ibikorwa ndetse, rimwe na rimwe, uburyo

29
00:01:44,964 --> 00:01:51,349
None ni ibihe byiza n'ibibi
byo kuba ufite patent?

30
00:01:51,754 --> 00:01:57,120
Noneho bwa nyuma, twaganiye gato ku burenganzira
bw'ibihangano bujyanye n'ibihangano b'ubuhanga

31
00:01:57,120 --> 00:02:02,657
ndetse tunaganira uko bukora,
hamwe na bimwe

32
00:02:02,657 --> 00:02:04,821
mu byiza n'ibibi
byabwo.

33
00:02:04,821 --> 00:02:10,227
Rero uzajye ubuzirikana, wibuka ko
ari kimwe mu bintu 

34
00:02:10,227 --> 00:02:12,825
bigize ububiko bwawe bwo kwigwizaho
amafaranga

35
00:02:13,103 --> 00:02:19,196
Kubera ko, nkuko mubyibuka, ikintu cya mbere 
ni ukubuza abandi kukwigana.

36
00:02:20,459 --> 00:02:24,887
Twahise twinjira mu gice cya kabiri
kugira tuganire ku mitungo y'inyongera.

37
00:02:25,162 --> 00:02:27,695
Iyo ikaba ikubiyemo buri kintu gikenewe
kugirango ucuruze

38
00:02:27,695 --> 00:02:31,416
agashya k'ikoranabuhanga
usibye iryo koranabuhanga ubwaryo.

39
00:02:32,295 --> 00:02:37,638
Ubwo twaboneye hamwe ingero zimwe na
zimwe zabyo, ndetse tunagira

40
00:02:37,638 --> 00:02:42,554
uburyo bwo kwibaza niba
tugomba kwita kuri iyo mitungo y'inyongera.

41
00:02:42,554 --> 00:02:45,254
Cyangwa se ni iyihe tugomba
kwitaho ndetse niba izatubuza

42
00:02:45,254 --> 00:02:49,663
gukorera amafaranga cyangwa ikadufasha
kugukorera amafaranga,

43
00:02:50,505 --> 00:02:52,456
maze birangira dufite 
iyi mbonerahamwe hano.

44
00:02:52,456 --> 00:02:55,257
Niba dufite hano 
ku ruhande rw'ibumoso

45
00:02:55,257 --> 00:03:00,285
dufite ububushobozi bwo kwiganwa
busobanuye ubushobozi

46
00:03:00,285 --> 00:03:06,256
bw'abo duhanganye--cyangw uwo ari we wese--
mu kwigana igicuruzwa cyangwa serivisi yawe

47
00:03:07,222 --> 00:03:13,742
guhera hasi kugera hejuru maze noneho,
ahagana ku ndiba tuvuga ku

48
00:03:13,742 --> 00:03:15,818
mitungo y'inyongera
ubwayo.

49
00:03:16,442 --> 00:03:19,398
Ese nta kamaro ifite cyangwa iboneka byoroshye?

50
00:03:19,528 --> 00:03:22,111
Mu yandi magambo, ntabwo uyitayeho

51
00:03:22,111 --> 00:03:26,611
cyangwa wakwandika kontaro byoroshye
usaba kuba wayihabwa.

52
00:03:26,768 --> 00:03:35,294
Cyangwa se niba ari ingenzi
kandi ikomeweho, bivuga ko

53
00:03:35,294 --> 00:03:40,271
ibigo by'ubucuruzi bike cyangwa kimwe
ari byo byonyine bifite iyo mitungo y'inyongera.

54
00:03:41,316 --> 00:03:48,127
Ubwo muri icyo gihe wowe, nk'umushoramari,
uzaba uri mu mwanya wa shoferi,

55
00:03:48,127 --> 00:03:54,107
nk'uko tubivuga, muri iki gice aho
biba bigoye kwigana ibyo uri gukora

56
00:03:54,107 --> 00:03:56,877
ndetse n'imitungo y'inyongera 
ikaba atari ingenzi cyangwa itaboneka byoroshye

57
00:03:56,953 --> 00:03:58,089
Ni aha ngaha

58
00:03:59,259 --> 00:04:02,575
Hari n'amahirwe ko 
wakura inyungu

59
00:04:02,575 --> 00:04:06,124
mu bihe bw'ubwigane buke.

60
00:04:07,629 --> 00:04:10,610
Nubwo haba hari umutungo ukomeweho.

61
00:04:13,070 --> 00:04:16,933
Kandi amahirwe menshi nuko 
ugihe gukura amafaranga menshi

62
00:04:16,933 --> 00:04:24,428
muri ubu buvumbuzi niba, koko
byoroshye kwigana ibyo wahimbye.

63
00:04:24,515 --> 00:04:27,570
Aha rero, nyiri wa mutungo w'inyongera
azabona amafaranga,

64
00:04:27,570 --> 00:04:29,579
kandi n'abakiriya bazabyungukiramo.

65
00:04:29,953 --> 00:04:33,212
Ntabwo ari ukuvuga ko 
aha ari ahantu habi ho kuba

66
00:04:33,212 --> 00:04:37,817
kubera ko gusa birebana n'uburyo
ushobora guhita ujya ku kindi gicuruzwa vuba.

67
00:04:38,711 --> 00:04:46,556
Ubwo rero, hano hejuru -mu gice cyo haruguru-
ushobra kuba wahimba ikintu runaka

68
00:04:46,556 --> 00:04:49,244
maze kikakubyarira amafaranga
mu gihe kirekire kurusha.

69
00:04:49,682 --> 00:04:52,674
Mu gice cyo hasi cy'iyi mbonerahamwe,
ushobora gukenera kwimuka 

70
00:04:52,674 --> 00:04:57,440
vuba uva ku buvumbizi bwawe
ujya ku bundi buvumbuzi

71
00:04:57,440 --> 00:04:59,427
kugira ngo ubashe kuzana
igicuruzwa gishya buri gihe.

72
00:04:59,593 --> 00:05:02,381
Ubwo rero urimo uriruka:
Gumana ubwo buryo bw'Isiganwa.

73
00:05:02,823 --> 00:05:08,705
Twahise twihutira mu kuganira ibibazo
by'amategeko birimo: ubwishingizi ni iki?

74
00:05:09,207 --> 00:05:13,182
Ni igihe uzaba wirengeye
ikintu runaka.

75
00:05:14,162 --> 00:05:19,721
Twaganiye ku bijyanye n'imigabane mu bigo 
by'imari: ni iyihe migabane uba ukeneye gutunga,

76
00:05:19,721 --> 00:05:22,808
kubera iki abayobozi n'abashinga ibigo
bagomba guhora bita ku migabane yabo,

77
00:05:22,808 --> 00:05:25,386
bigenda bite iyo umuntu avuye
mu kigo cy'imari cyany?

78
00:05:25,656 --> 00:05:28,993
Twaganiye ku mpapuro zirinda umutungo
w'ubwenge hanze y'igihugu cyawe.

79
00:05:28,993 --> 00:05:31,837
None ni uwuhe mugambi wawe
ufite mu ikoranabuhanga mpuzamahanga?

80
00:05:32,273 --> 00:05:37,450
Twaganiye ku ma kontaro yokudahangana,
 ubwishingizi bw'ibicuruzwa

81
00:05:37,450 --> 00:05:42,201
ndetse n'ibyo ugomba kugenderaho
ushaka umunyamategeko.

82
00:05:42,954 --> 00:05:47,458
Noneho muri aka gace ka nyuma,
twaganiye gato ku guhira ibintu hagati.

83
00:05:48,509 --> 00:05:52,528
Icyo bivuga n'ighe
ushobora gukenera kubikora.

84
00:05:52,869 --> 00:05:57,931
Hano, ni mugihe, ibyo 
wakekaga mbere atari byo.

85
00:05:57,957 --> 00:06:01,529
Iyo abantu biri kubagora
kwishyura mu gihe wateganyaga,

86
00:06:01,529 --> 00:06:05,930
Iyo ibintu biri guhinduka hafi yawe,
iyo ibicuruzwa byawe biri gutinda kugurishwa,

87
00:06:06,052 --> 00:06:11,488
Icyo ni ikimenyetso ko ugomba guhindura 
imwe mu mikorere y'ubucuruzi bwawe

88
00:06:11,488 --> 00:06:15,518
kugira ngo ubyaze umusaruro ibyo
bikenerwa biri hariya.

89
00:06:15,641 --> 00:06:21,518
Twaganiye ku kwagura. Ibyo bivuga 
kongera umubare w'ibicuruzwa

90
00:06:21,518 --> 00:06:23,777
Ukoresheje ibikoresho bimwe.

91
00:06:23,937 --> 00:06:27,541
Turangije twaganiye gato ku byo
wakora kugira ngo ibyo ubigereho.

92
00:06:27,541 --> 00:06:28,944
Ugomba guhera ku musozo.

93
00:06:28,944 --> 00:06:32,150
Ukeneye kubanza wareba neza
ko amafaranga byagutwara

94
00:06:32,150 --> 00:06:34,937
Kugira ngo wongere ibucuruzwa ari make.

95
00:06:35,458 --> 00:06:39,876
Ugomba no kumanza wakora ku buryo
imiterere y'ikigo ubwayo yakwakira imikurire.


96
00:06:40,836 --> 00:06:46,557
ibyo bikaba bituyoboye kuri iyi mbonerahamwe
ya nyuma hano, aho twaganiye ku mubano

97
00:06:46,557 --> 00:06:50,601
hagati y'ubunini bw'ikigo 
n'imyaka ikigo kimaze

98
00:06:50,601 --> 00:06:53,404
n'ibyiciro bitandukanye
icyo kigo 

99
00:06:53,404 --> 00:06:58,875
cyinyuramo iyo kiri gukura
kiba kinini kurusha.

100
00:06:58,875 --> 00:07:04,859
Niba mwibuka guhera muri iyi mbonerahamwe,
no mu biganira byacy, ikigo

101
00:07:04,859 --> 00:07:10,282
--ikigo cy'imari kikivuka--kiva mu
kuba umuryango uyobowe n'abawushinze

102
00:07:10,282 --> 00:07:15,252
mu ntangiriro, wagiye unyura mu bibazo
byinshi mu bihe bitandukanye,

103
00:07:15,252 --> 00:07:21,120
kigahinduka ikigo cy'imari kibowe
ku buryo bw'uruhererekane,

104
00:07:21,120 --> 00:07:24,811
kiba ari kinini cyane kurusha
kandi gifite imikurire iri hejuru.

105
00:07:25,483 --> 00:07:27,820
Ngibyo ibyo twaganiye muri ibi byumweru bitanu.

106
00:07:27,820 --> 00:07:30,820
Mwitegure kubona inshamake

107
00:07:30,820 --> 00:07:34,259
y'isomo ryose Marc
nanjye tuzakora ubutaha.
